"},{"pid":"904ecf8facf08220b8b65c5453cb25541f938647","tid":1094061,"uid":17215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"咁個黑衣男捉咗未?"},{"pid":"e603cce8a9da5dd7f4ad22239f86cd972a7994c0","tid":1094061,"uid":192078,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"acf00584a9ba3e2fa80eb15825789b1ad6b4d94d","tid":1094061,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"選樣最痛既黎自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"三島隨後從陽台退入室內，按照日本傳統儀式切腹自殺。三島由紀夫在額際繫上了寫著「七生報國」字樣的頭巾，用白色的布將預備切腹的部位一圈圈緊緊地裹住，<span style=\"color: red;\">拿起短刀往自己的腹部刺下，割出了一個很大的傷口，腸子從傷口流出來</span>。<span style=\"color: pink;\">隨他同來的兩位盾會成員之一的森田必勝用名刀「關孫六」為三島進行介錯</span>，但<span style=\"color: red;\">因害怕手軟連砍三次都未能斬下他的頭顱，三島由紀夫忍著痛楚，沉吼低呼著：「再砍！再砍！使力！」</span>，第四次介錯改由學習過居合道的盾會成員古賀浩靖執行，終於成功。之後森田必勝也切腹自殺～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85215bf22392df028412146538c7d436591766a9","tid":1094061,"uid":131245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9ce93a55beae8f36f48842830b716814934d0b0","tid":1094061,"uid":192078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0865e4f766948480dd670f29dcd835d9254cb6aa","tid":1094061,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6609d819837be9077d4f3c056ddb404b2c2f534a","tid":1094061,"uid":91778,"like":1815,"dislike":4,"score":1811,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"切腹係需要無比嘅勇氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"你估佢係三島由紀夫咩！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"佢都頂唔順呀～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"要搵人介錯架"},{"pid":"25f9251bec7b6fb393